title: [Grawood Farmstead, Field]
description: Listing about aimlessly on the other side of the fence, a tawny tan and white cow has settled beneath the branches of a well-pruned apple tree.  Despite the cool beneath the shade of the tree, the cow's tail whips back and forth, swatting at flies that disturb its rest.
room.location: Grawood Farmstead outside of River's Rest
